{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a matter of getting better job, because on that kind of job, where I had unloading bricks or digging trenches, I knew I will not survive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had an information given that there is a good job going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew the-- the-- what they call Arbeitsdienst, in German, who gave the work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to live-- we've been-- he's been in the same prison as I was in Sanok.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ask him if I can get-- there is a vacancy at the rabbit feeding company, breeding company.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told me, well, I know you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can give you that job with your brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I got that job, which was a lot easier, because sometimes I could get some food what the rabbits had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was warm on the roof, which made me easier to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long did you continue doing that job with the rabbits?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was doing the job for the first-- well, I-- they moved us from Auschwitz to another kommando outside Auschwitz, where we were living in a Harmeze Schule, special school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, we-- we started living all together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they also opened a farm house there, chicken farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a fishery farm for-- for crop fish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where all the people were moved into one place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people from fishing camp, they were moved to another place, where was someone was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Harmensee, that was the village name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- there was a big house, used to be former palace of [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Zwilling ?], [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zwilling ?] man, he had a big palace, where we lived at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
